                  "paragraphTitle": "What makes a good advert?",
                  "paragraphSubtitles": [
                    ""
                  ],
                  "paragraphContents": [
                    "A good advertisement must catch your eye. It needs to be original and needs to grab your attention. It needs to make you stop and look at it. The image should also be something the viewer can connect with on a personal level. A good advert also needs to have a clear and simple message and also have a catchy slogan, such as Nike's 'Just do it' or Microsoft's 'Where do you want to go today?' It should also have the company name or logo on the advert somewhere. But above all, the advert needs to tell you that the product or brand is the best there is and it needs to make you go and buy it."
                  ]
